  "body": "In federation e2e tests we do use LoadBalancer type of service for all needs.\r\nCreating LoadBalancer type of service for every test case is kind of expensive and time consuming to provision. Thus making the overall test-suite little slower.\r\n\r\nWe could use ClusterIp type of services wherever we don't exactly need the service to be a LoadBalancer type.\r\n\r\n/cc @madhusudancs \r\n/sig federation",
